</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-lnPyOc gUmbDa pf-1066_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Practical_Resuscitation_Training_Courses_in_London_Book_Now_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1727510915" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Practical_Resuscitation_Training_Courses_in_London_Book_Now_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1727510915 1536w" width="1419" height="946" alt="Practical Resuscitation Training Courses in London: Book Now - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Practical Resuscitation Training Courses in London: Book Now - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gdyfxU iluFjz pf-1063_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-1065_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by LightFieldStudios via Envato Elements</p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-f4c4" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-dxcExB gjNMyZ pf-1235_ pf-color-scheme-1 pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-kqGpvY OSjcf"><div class="sc-dhKdPU hjOBND pf-1077_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-lnPyOc gUmbDa pf-1076_"><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-1075_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">In healthcare and social care settings, knowing how to perform effective Basic Life Support (BLS) is more than just a regulatory requirement—it's a critical skill that can mean the difference between life and death. Whether you’re a seasoned healthcare professional or new to the field, ensuring your BLS skills are up to date is essential. At The Mandatory Training Group, we offer comprehensive practical resuscitation courses designed to meet compliance standards and truly prepare you for real-world emergencies. Our expert-led training sessions, available weekly in London, Coventry, and Manchester, provide the hands-on experience needed to act confidently in any emergency situation.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-dhKdPU hjOBND pf-1093_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-lnPyOc gUmbDa pf-1088_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-brPMkR cnEYUf pf-1079_ pf-heading-1-h3">Key definitions
</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Join_Our_Practical_Resuscitation_Training_-_Available_for_Immediate_Booking_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1727510676" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Join_Our_Practical_Resuscitation_Training_-_Available_for_Immediate_Booking_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1727510676 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Join_Our_Practical_Resuscitation_Training_-_Available_for_Immediate_Booking_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1000x.jpg?v=1727510676 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Join_Our_Practical_Resuscitation_Training_-_Available_for_Immediate_Booking_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.jpg?v=1727510676 320w" width="1000" height="1500" alt="Join Our Practical Resuscitation Training - Available for Immediate Booking  - The Mandatory Training Group UK -.jpg__PID:eecd8dc8-9dd2-4afb-bcd4-91b6523c6772" title="Join Our Practical Resuscitation Training - Available for Immediate Booking  - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gdyfxU iluFjz pf-1089_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-1091_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by  LightFieldStudios via Envato Elements</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-brPMkR cnEYUf pf-1081_ pf-heading-1-h3">What is basic life support (BLS)?
</h3><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-1083_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Basic Life Support (BLS) refers to the level of medical care used for victims of life-threatening illnesses or injuries until they can be given full medical care at a hospital. It includes techniques such as cardiopulmonary resuscitation (CPR) and using an Automated External Defibrillator (AED).
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-brPMkR cnEYUf pf-1085_ pf-heading-1-h3">Adult and paediatric basic life support
</h3><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-1087_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">While based on the same principles, adult BLS and paediatric BLS differ in application due to variations in anatomy and physiology between adults and children. This training ensures that professionals can effectively respond to cardiac emergencies in both adults and children.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-dhKdPU hjOBND pf-1110_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-lnPyOc gUmbDa pf-1109_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-brPMkR cnEYUf pf-1099_ pf-heading-1-h3">Key facts and statistics</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Unlocking_Innovation_A_Guide_to_Measuring_Success_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_ee69602d-1c85-4a76-a511-e0fd02aabb8a.jpg?v=1727437349" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Unlocking_Innovation_A_Guide_to_Measuring_Success_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_ee69602d-1c85-4a76-a511-e0fd02aabb8a.jpg?v=1727437349 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Unlocking_Innovation_A_Guide_to_Measuring_Success_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_ee69602d-1c85-4a76-a511-e0fd02aabb8a_1500x.jpg?v=1727437349 1280w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Unlocking_Innovation_A_Guide_to_Measuring_Success_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_ee69602d-1c85-4a76-a511-e0fd02aabb8a_1000x.jpg?v=1727437349 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Unlocking_Innovation_A_Guide_to_Measuring_Success_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_ee69602d-1c85-4a76-a511-e0fd02aabb8a_500x.jpg?v=1727437349 320w" width="1548" height="1179" alt="Reserve Your Spot: Practical Resuscitation Courses Now Open - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " title="Reserve Your Spot: Practical Resuscitation Courses Now Open - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gdyfxU iluFjz pf-1094_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-1096_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by Rawpixel via Envato Elements</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-EROOM foKNLL pf-1108_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-dNsUpz eAuVCY pf-1101_ pf-text-1"><strong>Heart attacks in the UK </strong>- Each year, approximately 100,000 hospital admissions are due to heart attacks, which equates to one every five minutes.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-dNsUpz eAuVCY pf-1103_ pf-text-1"><strong>Cardiac arrests </strong>- Around 30,000 out-of-hospital cardiac arrests (OHCA) occur annually in the UK, with survival rates currently at less than 10%.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-dNsUpz eAuVCY pf-1105_ pf-text-1"><strong>Importance of CPR</strong> - Immediate CPR can double or triple the chances of survival after cardiac arrest.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-dNsUpz eAuVCY pf-1107_ pf-text-1"><strong>Refresher training benefits </strong>- Studies show that skills and knowledge acquired in BLS training can degrade within a few months. Regular refresher courses are essential to maintain proficiency and confidence.
</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-dhKdPU hjOBND pf-1136_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-lnPyOc gUmbDa pf-1131_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-brPMkR cnEYUf pf-1112_ pf-heading-1-h3">Debunking myths about basic life support
